command: from worldsim.stats import StatsCollector; from worldsim.types import StepResult, WorldState, Position, Agent; ws = WorldState(5, 5, 1, 42, ((Position(0,0), Agent(10, 1, 0)),)); sr = StepResult(world=ws, births=1, deaths=2, movements=3); sc = StatsCollector(); tm = sc.record(sr); assert tm.population == 1 and tm.births == 1 and tm.deaths == 2 and tm.avg_energy == 10.0 and abs(tm.density - 1/25) < 1e-9

from worldsim.stats import StatsCollector; from worldsim.types import StepResult, WorldState; ws = WorldState(5, 5, 0, 42, ()); sr = StepResult(world=ws, births=0, deaths=0, movements=0); sc = StatsCollector(); sc.record(sr); csv = sc.to_csv(); assert 'step_number' in csv and 'density' in csv; lines = csv.strip().split(chr(10)); assert len(lines) == 2
